title: V01 — A Single Room
story: familyzoo
author: Sharpee Tutorial
description: Verify that the Zoo Entrance room exists with scenery objects

---

# V1 teaches: look and examine in a single room

# The game starts at the Zoo Entrance
> look
[OK: contains "Zoo Entrance"]
[OK: contains "Willowbrook Family Zoo"]
[OK: contains "welcome sign"]
[OK: contains "ticket booth"]

# Examine the welcome sign
> examine sign
[OK: contains "WELCOME TO WILLOWBROOK"]

# Examine the ticket booth
> examine booth
[OK: contains "Self-Guided Tours"]

# Scenery can't be taken
> take sign
[OK: contains "fixed in place"]

# Try looking again to confirm the room is stable
> look
[OK: contains "Zoo Entrance"]
